  <bioghist id="aspace_63144bc350bc7b072118a539d8f4aecc">
    <head>Biography</head>
<p>Starting in the 1970's, Marjorie Thompson Duck worked in support of environmentalist causes of both national and local importance to Eastern Pennsylvania.  Her personal interest in clean energy led to her involvement in an organization dedicated to environmental outreach in local schools.  In the organization Mrs. Duck served as librarian and collected educational materials.  The name of the organization and the exact time frame of Ms. Duck's involvement is not known.</p>  </bioghist>
