  <scopecontent id="aspace_22509872b07c30995da47cb2db78e0bc">
    <head>Scope and Content Notes</head>
<p>The Marjorie T. Duck Environmental Collection consists predominately of publications and printed material on issues related to energy production and the proposed installation of a hazardous waste incinerator in Allenwood, Pennsylvania.  The materials range in date from 1973 to 1995.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <arrangement id="aspace_e904fe3df2134e823e3901b6fa6e3d51">
    <head>Arrangement</head>
<p>The Marge Duck Environmental Collection is arranged into two series:</p><p>Series I. Energy, 1973-1991</p><p>Series II. Hazardous Waste Incinerator, 1986-1995</p>  </arrangement>
